      • annotated

        public FieldSignature<T> annotated(java.util.Collection<? extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation> annotations)
        Description copied from interface: AnnotatedSignature
        Derive a version of this declaration with the given annotations. Users should take care not to specify annotations which could not be applied to the declaration due to their Target, as there is no validation of applicability.

        Annotations already present on the receiving declaration will be replaced rather than appended.

        Specified by:
